\c 1
\s Ukulingwa kukaJobe lokubekezela kwakhe
\p
\v 1 Kwakukhona indoda elizweni leUzi\x + Jer. 25.20. Lilo 4.21. Gen. 10.23,22.21,36.28. 1 Lan. 1.17,42.\x*, ibizo layo lalinguJobe\x + Hez. 14.14,20. Jak. 5.11.\x*. Leyondoda yayiphelele-ke, iqondile\x + 9.8. 2.3. Gen. 17.1.\x*, imesaba uNkulunkulu\x + Zaga 16.6.\x*, ixwaya okubi\x + Hlab. 34.14.\x*.
\v 2 Yasizalelwa amadodana ayisikhombisa lamadodakazi amathathu.
\v 3 Lemfuyo yayo yayiyizimvu eziyizinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa, lamakamela ayizinkulungwane ezintathu, lezipane zenkabi ezingamakhulu amahlanu, labobabhemi abasikazi abangamakhulu amahlanu, lenceku ezinengi kakhulu. Ngakho lowomuntu wayemkhulu okwedlula bonke abantu bempumalanga.
\p
\v 4 Njalo amadodana akhe ahamba enza idili endlini yaleyo laleyo ngosuku lwayo\x + Esta 1.3.\x*; athuma abiza odadewabo abathathu ukuze badle banathe lawo\x + Esta 5.12.\x*.
\v 5 Kwakusithi lapho esephelile amazopha ensuku zedili, uJobe athume, awangcwelise, avuke ekuseni kakhulu, anikele iminikelo yokutshiswa \add ngokw\add*enani lawo wonke\x + 42.8. Gen. 8.20.\x*, ngoba uJobe wathi: Mhlawumbe amadodana ami onile, amthuka\f + \fk amthuka: \fl Heb. \fq ambusisa.\f* uNkulunkulu enhliziyweni yawo\x + 1.11. 2.5,9. 1 Kho. 21.10,13.\x*. Wenza njalo uJobe zonke izinsuku.
\p
\v 6 Kwasekusiba losuku\x + 1.13. 2.1. 1 Sam. 1.4. 2 Kho. 4.8,11,18.\x* lapho amadodana kaNkulunkulu eza ukuzimisa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, loSathane laye wafika phakathi kwawo\x + Gen. 6.2,4. 2.1. 38.7. 1 Kho. 22.19. Hlab. 89.5-7.\x*.
\v 7 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuSathane: Uvela ngaphi? USathane wasephendula iN\nd kosi\nd* wathi: Ekuzulazuleni emhlabeni lekuhambahambeni kuwo\x + 2.2. 2 Sam. 24.2. 1 Pet. 5.8.\x*.
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuSathane: Ubekile yini inhliziyo yakho encekwini yami uJobe, ngoba kakho onjengayo emhlabeni, umuntu opheleleyo loqondileyo, owesaba uNkulunkulu loxwaya ububi\x + 1.1.\x*?
\v 9 USathane wasephendula iN\nd kosi\nd* wathi: UJobe umesabela ize uNkulunkulu yini?
\v 10 Kawumbiyelanga yini yena lendlu yakhe lakho konke alakho inhlangothi zonke\x + 10.11.\x*? Ubusisile umsebenzi wezandla zakhe\x + Hlab. 128.1,2.\x*, lezifuyo zakhe zanda kakhulu elizweni\x + Gen. 28.14.\x*.
\v 11 Kodwa isibili yelula isandla sakho khathesi, uthinte konke alakho\x + 2.5. 19.21.\x*; sibili uzakuthuka\f + \fk ukuthuka: \fl Heb. \fq ukubusisa.\f* ebusweni bakho\x + 13.15. Isa. 65.3. Dute. 7.10.\x*.
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuSathane: Khangela konke alakho kusesandleni sakho; kuphela kuye ungeluleli isandla sakho. Wasephuma uSathane phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 13 Kwasekusiba losuku\x + 1.13. 2.1. 1 Sam. 1.4. 2 Kho. 4.8,11,18.\x* lapho amadodana lamadodakazi akhe ayesidla enatha iwayini endlini yomfowabo olizibulo\x + 1.5,18.\x*.
\v 14 Kwasekufika isithunywa kuJobe sathi: Inkabi bezilima labobabhemi besidla emaceleni azo;
\v 15 kwasekutheleka amaShebha, akuthatha, atshaya izinceku ngobukhali benkemba, njalo yimi ngedwa kuphela engiphephileyo ukuze ngikubikele\x + 1 Kho. 10.1.\x*.
\v 16 Lesi sisakhuluma, kwafika lesinye, sathi: Umlilo kaNkulunkulu uwile uvela emazulwini, watshisa izimvu lezinceku, waziqeda; njalo yimi ngedwa kuphela engiphephileyo ukuze ngikubikele.
\v 17 Lesi sisakhuluma, kwafika lesinye, sathi: AmaKhaladiya\x + Gen. 11.28. 2 Kho. 24.2. Dan. 1.4. 2.2.\x* amise amaxuku\x + 1 Lan. 12.23.\x* amathathu\x + Hlu. 7.16. 1 Sam. 11.11. Gen. 14.15.\x* atheleka phezu kwamakamela, awathatha, atshaya izinceku ngobukhali benkemba, njalo yimi ngedwa kuphela engiphephileyo ukuze ngikubikele.
\v 18 Lesi sisakhuluma, kwafika lesinye, sathi: Amadodana akho lamadodakazi akho bebesidla benatha iwayini endlini yomfowabo, izibulo\x + 1.4,13.\x*.
\v 19 Khangela-ke, umoya omkhulu wafika uvela ngaphetsheya kwenkangala, watshaya amagumbi womane endlu, yawela phezu kwamajaha, afa; njalo yimi ngedwa kuphela engiphephileyo ukuze ngikubikele\x + Isa. 21.1. Jer. 4.11. Hos. 13.15.\x*.
\v 20 UJobe wasesukuma\x + Jona 3.6.\x*, wadabula ibhatshi lakhe\x + Gen. 44.13.\x*, waphuca ikhanda lakhe, wawa emhlabathini, wakhonza\x + Jer. 7.29. Mika 1.16. Isa. 15.2. 22.12. Jer. 16.6. 47.5. 48.37. Hez. 7.18. Levi 21.5. Ezra 9.3.\x*;
\v 21 wasesithi: Ngaphuma ngize esiswini sikamama, njalo ngizabuyela khona ngize\x + Tshu. 5.15. 1 Tim. 6.7.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 12.9.\x* yapha\x + Tshu. 5.19. Jak. 1.17.\x*, iN\nd kosi\nd* ithethe; kalibusiswe ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Hlab. 113.2. Dan. 2.20.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Kukho konke lokhu uJobe konanga, kambalelanga ubuwula uNkulunkulu\x + 2.10.\x*.